/*:
 * @target MZ
 * @plugindesc [CF Patch] DotMove-compatible patch for CF_BattleSkillCombo
 * @author CFpanda
 * @url https://cfpanda.itch.io/
 *
 * @help
 * ============================================================================
 * CF_BattleSkillCombo_DotMovePatch
 * ============================================================================
 * Place this plugin BELOW these plugins:
 * - DotMoveSystem
 * - CF_Attack
 * - CF_AttackObject
 * - CF_PlayerActionMotion
 * - CF_PlayerSkillCast
 * - CF_BattleSkillCombo
 *
 * This patch makes CF_BattleSkillCombo safer with the current MZ movement and
 * battle flow:
 * - Uses 8-direction interaction direction when available.
 * - Supports DotMove-style half coordinates during dash scan.
 * - Prevents skill / normal attack input while combo dash is busy.
 * - Keeps final attack generation inside the original queueAttackObject flow.
 * - Waits for CF_PlayerActionMotion pending attack objects before unlocking.
 *
 * Skill note remains:
 * <comboDash>
